Hi Community / dev team,

As PMC Chair and VP of Apache Grails, I’d like to request adding Grails 
to the official ASF TeePublic store 
(https://www.teepublic.com/user/the-apache-software-foundation).

We have the official high-resolution Grails logo ready here 
https://www.apache.org/logos/#grails. A simple logo t-shirt in the same 
style as the existing ones would be perfect to start.

We would love to be wearing these at Community over Code 2026.

I’m happy to review logo placement or provide anything else needed.

Thanks,
James Fredley
PMC Chair / VP, Apache Grails

